    base:desc "Continuous real‑time synchronization between the physical building and its digital twin is achieved through the framework’s real‑time data exchange capabilities. The system continuously pushes sensor measurements from the physical assets to the digital replica and pulls control commands back, ensuring a near‑zero‑lag loop. While explicit update frequencies or latency bounds are not specified in the documents, the architecture emphasizes continuous, low‑latency data flow to support live monitoring, predictive analytics, and rapid control decisions."
