instance dt_constellation : DTDFVocab:Constellation [
    base:desc "Model‑driven deployment orchestrates an end‑to‑end lifecycle: enriched BIM data is parsed via MDE to generate structured digital twins for each physical component; a central DT framework hub orchestrates bidirectional data exchange, runtime configuration, and service plug‑in integration; the architecture follows a hub‑and‑spoke pattern with the central hub coordinating device‑level sub‑twin instances, encapsulating device modeling, control logic, and monitoring; resource management and coordination are handled by this central component, while DT Engineers extend functionality through standardized extension points."
